snippet.title: Sonic: Project Survival SAGE 2016 Demo Release
snippet.description:
Download the demo here: http://gamejolt.com/games/sonic-project-survival-sage-2016-demo/199383

Sonic returns to his roots in Sonic: Project Survival, a fan game developed by Team Survival which pays homage to 2D Classic Sonic gameplay with an accurate physics engine that allows players to blast through levels at high speed!

Trailer created by DanRock: https://www.youtube.com/user/roadrunner8855
